{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1693-10a_049","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Allegorie","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", octobre 1693 [tome 12], p. 49-54.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":[{},"Le Roy a accordé depuis peu de temps des Lettres Patentes à une Abbesse d’un fort grand merite, &amp; d’une naissance distinguée, pour quitter un lieu champestre, où son Convent estoit situé, &amp; se venir établir dans la Capitale d’une Province. C’est là-dessus qu’on a fait l’Ouvrage que vous allez lire."],"quote":{"label":{"value":"ALLEGORIE.","id":"/div/quote/label"},"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des Abeilles, Filles du Ciel,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Depuis longtemps faisoient leur miel","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans un lieu desert &amp; sauvage.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Une Reine discrete &amp; sage,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans orgueil, sans faste &amp; sans fiel,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Presidoit seule à tout l’Ouvrage.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chacune respectoit la loy","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une si douce Souveraine.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un autre l’appelleroit Roy ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il est mieux de l’appeller Reine.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À des Vierges, Filles des Cieux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Une Reine sied beaucoup mieux.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sous cette Reine nompareille","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On voyoit mainte &amp; mainte Abeilles","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Accourir de tout l’Univers,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et dans un si charmant Empire","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Goûter des plaisirs que mes Vers","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne sçauroient dignement décrire.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour comble de felicité,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Auprés d’elle une jeune Abeille,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[19]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pleine de grace &amp; de beauté,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enfin, une jeune Merveille","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Croissoit ainsi qu’un rejetton,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ou d’une rose le bouton.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’or dont la Souveraine brille,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[24]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Brilloit déja sur cette Fille,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[25]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et chacune la destinoit","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[26]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au rang que la Tante tenoit.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[27]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un jour de la saison nouvelle,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[28]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jour, où sur les fleurs d’alentour","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[29]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Voloit la Troupe tour a tour,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[30]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du Ciel une Abeille immortelle","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[31]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’éleve d’un rapide cours,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[32]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ainsi qu’un éclair dans la nuë,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[33]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et prés de la Reine venuë,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[34]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Luy tient à peu prés ce discours.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[35]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dieu vous gard, aimable Princesse,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[36]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’ay pensé dire, aimable Abbesse,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Digne de regner en des lieux","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[38]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus fleuris, plus delicieux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Digne enfin de regner aux Cieux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[40]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ecoutez ce que vous commande","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[41]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Souverain de vostre bande,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[42]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et Souverain de l’Univers.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[43]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nimphe, abandonnez ces deserts,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[44]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Allez chercher dans une Ville","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[45]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un sejour qui soit plus tranquille,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[46]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui soit plus commode &amp; plus doux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[47]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Digne des vostres &amp; de vous.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[48]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est là que les destins propices","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[49]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous préparent tant de delices,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[50]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que vos vœux seront surpassez,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[51]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est assez dit, obeissez.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[52]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aussi-tost d’une aile legere","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[53]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cette charmante Messagere,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[54]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Traçant un sillon radieux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[55]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’envole par dessus les Cieux.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[56]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Surprise de tant de merveilles,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[57]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Reine avecque ses Abeilles ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[58]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nous obeissons à tes loix,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[59]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ciel, dit elle, &amp; suivons ta voix.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[60]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Adorons cet heureux présage,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[61]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mes Sœurs, mettons-nous en voyage,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[62]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Allons chercher ce beau sejour,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[63]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que le Ciel nous offre en ce jour.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[64]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A ces mots la Troupe s’assemble,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[65]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout l’Essain part &amp; vole ensemble.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[66]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’air brille d’un éclat nouveau,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[67]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et ravy d’un objet si beau,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[68]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De nouveaux rayons de lumiere","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[69]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Soleil pare sa carriere.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[70]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Zephir les regarde voler,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[71]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et tout charmé n’ose soufler.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[72]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chaque Abeille à l’envy s’empresse","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[73]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’approcher de prés sa Maistresse.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[74]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si-tost que le sejour paroît,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[75]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que le destin luy préparoit,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[76]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Non loin des rives de Garonne,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[77]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Princesse dispose, ordonne.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[78]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Toute la Troupe arreste là,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[79]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chante de joye,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[80]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":" Alleluia.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[80]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chacune en l’ardeur qui la brûle","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[81]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Travaille à faire sa cellule,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[82]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À remplir sa ruche de fleurs,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[83]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À l’embaumer de mille odeurs.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[84]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Abeilles du voisinage","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[85]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cependant leur rendent hommage,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[86]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sortent de leur ruche à dessein","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[87]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’admirer ce nouvel Essain,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[88]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le trouvent charmant à merveilles,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[89]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et le plus beau que les Abeilles","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[90]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aient formé dans ce beau sejour,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[91]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et dans tous les lieux d’alentour,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[92]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Parlent du doux air qu’on respire","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[93]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans ce doux &amp; charmant Empire,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[94]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De sa douceur, de son plaisir,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[95]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que mes Vers diront à loisir.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[96]/#"}}]}}}}